00:32:29.480 --> 00:32:32.759
that are also available to all users of the system.

00:32:32.759 --> 00:32:39.930
But what's nice is that you're able to change those on the
back end in one place, but every user has access to those,

00:32:39.930 --> 00:32:49.390
and it could be anything, fonts,
system resources of any type.

